Ruth White (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruth_White_(actress) 0 Ruth Patricia White (April 24, 1914 – December 3, 1969) was an American actress who worked in theatre, film, and television. She was an Emmy Award and Obie Award winner and also a Tony Award nominee.
